<title>USA: Informix target of lawsuit -- attorneys.</title>
<headline>Informix target of lawsuit -- attorneys.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-16</dateline>
<text>
<p>Attorneys for purchasers of common stock of Informix Corp during a one-year period said Friday a complaint seeking class action status has been filed against the company.</p>
<p>The attorneys said the complaint was filed by plaintiff Sallie Felzen on her behalf and on behalf of purchasers of common stock between March 29, 1996 and April 2, 1997.</p>
<p>A spokesman for the law firm of Stamell &amp; Schrager LLP said the suit is one of several class action suits filed against the company.</p>
